title: Spider-Man Mega Collection - Part 05 (of 06) (- Nem -)
description:
Spider-Man Mega Collection - Part 05 (of 06)

This part of the collection is my favorite - lots of 

goodies - Trading Cards, collected Daily Newspaper 

Strips, Audio, A folder of Freebies/GiveAways, Over 

300 Marvel UK Spidey Issues, Marvel Zombies, Superior 

Spider-Man and plenty more. There`s still another 

part to this collection to come.

I forgot to add the .txt to Spidey05 but needless to 

say A huge thanks goes out to all the scanners and 

rippers out there - without whom none of this would 

even be possible.

Also a well derserved Thankyou to AnimeHunt for 

supplying me with his entire Spidey Collection to 

share, I located all the Marvel UK issues and a few 

other bits n pieces, and to finish things off 

uploaded and shared - Enjoy.
